Package com.wedriveu.services.vehicle.rabbitmq

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Constants  
    Messages
    Represents the message addresses used between Verticles inside the VehicleService.
    Messages.Analytics  
    Messages.Booking  
    Messages.BookingControl  
    Messages.NearestControl
    Addresses used by the Messages.NearestControl Verticle to handle the requests used at the beginning of vehicle election process.
    Messages.VehicleFinder
    Address used by the Messages.VehicleFinder Verticle to lookup vehicles that can actually make the trip.
    Messages.VehicleRegister
    Address used by the Messages.VehicleRegister Verticle to receive new vehicle register requests from the vehicle itself.
    Messages.VehicleService
    Address used at the application startup from the Main class to start the BootVerticle Verticle.
    Messages.VehicleStore
    Addresses used by the Messages.VehicleStore Verticle to handle db requests and responses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SubstitutionRequest
    Created by Michele on 19/08/2017.
    UserRequest
    Represents the data the client sends when requesting the best vehicle to book as well as the list of available vehicles at the time of the request.
